\end{array}
@EndMath
@EndifDoc
@EndDescription
@EndOperator


@BeginExample
To compute the seasonally mean over all input years, use:
@BeginVerbatim
   cdo yseasmean ifile ofile
@EndVerbatim
@EndExample
